---
title: BeaconLink Canary Deployment
---

flowchart LR

    %% =====================================================
    %% Existing Production
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Stable["Stable Environment"]

        StableApp["Application v1"]
        StableHealth["Healthy Production"]

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Canary Environment
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Canary["Canary Environment"]

        CanaryDeploy["Deploy Application v2"]
        CanaryConfig["Apply Configuration"]
        CanarySecrets["Inject Secrets"]
        CanaryHealth["Health Verification"]

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Deployment Pipeline
    %% =====================================================

    Manifest["Deployment Revision"]

    Planner["Deployment Planner"]

    Scheduler["Distributed Scheduler"]

    Relay["Relay Network"]

    Agent["BeaconLink Agent"]

    Runtime["Runtime Adapter"]

    Manifest --> Planner
    Planner --> Scheduler
    Scheduler --> Relay
    Relay --> Agent
    Agent --> Runtime

    Runtime --> CanaryDeploy

    CanaryDeploy --> CanaryConfig
    CanaryConfig --> CanarySecrets
    CanarySecrets --> CanaryHealth

    %% =====================================================
    %% Traffic Management
    %% =====================================================

    Users["Users"]

    Gateway["API Gateway"]

    Traffic["Traffic Router"]

    Users --> Gateway
    Gateway --> Traffic

    Traffic --> StableApp
    Traffic --> CanaryDeploy

    %% =====================================================
    %% Progressive Rollout
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Progression["Traffic Progression"]

        Five["5%"]
        Ten["10%"]
        TwentyFive["25%"]
        Fifty["50%"]
        Hundred["100%"]

        Five --> Ten
        Ten --> TwentyFive
        TwentyFive --> Fifty
        Fifty --> Hundred

    end

    CanaryHealth --> Five

    %% =====================================================
    %% Validation
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Validation["Continuous Validation"]

        Health["Health Checks"]
        Metrics["Performance Metrics"]
        Errors["Error Rates"]
        Latency["Latency"]
        Policies["Policy Compliance"]

    end

    Five --> Health
    Ten --> Health
    TwentyFive --> Health
    Fifty --> Health

    Health --> Metrics
    Metrics --> Errors
    Errors --> Latency
    Latency --> Policies

    %% =====================================================
    %% Promotion Decision
    %% =====================================================

    Decision{"Validation Successful?"}

    Policies --> Decision

    Decision -->|Yes| Promote["Increase Traffic"]

    Promote --> Hundred

    Hundred --> Complete["Promote to Production"]

    %% =====================================================
    %% Rollback
    %% =====================================================

    Decision -->|No| Rollback["Remove Canary"]

    Rollback --> StableApp

    %% =====================================================
    %% Completion
    %% =====================================================

    Cleanup["Retire Previous Revision"]

    Complete --> Cleanup

    %% =====================================================
    %% Audit
    %% =====================================================

    Audit["Audit Trail"]

    Events["Platform Events"]

    Cleanup --> Audit
    Rollback --> Audit

    Audit --> Events

    %% =====================================================
    %% Canary Evaluation Criteria
    %% =====================================================

    Criteria["Promotion Criteria

• Health Checks Pass
• Error Rate Acceptable
• Latency Within SLA
• Resource Usage Stable
• Policy Validation
• No Drift Detected
• Operator Approval (Optional)"]

    Criteria -.-> Validation

    %% =====================================================
    %% Principles
    %% =====================================================

    Principles["Canary Principles

• Progressive Delivery
• Controlled Exposure
• Continuous Monitoring
• Automated Promotion
• Automated Rollback
• Risk Reduction
• Immutable Revisions"]

    Principles -.-> Canary
    Principles -.-> Progression
    Principles -.-> Validation

